{"word":"φανός","slug":"φανός","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>φανός1</b></el> <el>(φᾱνός, ή, όν) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:φαίνω'><el>φαίνω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>light, bright</i>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b>:— <el>τὸ φανόν</el> <i>brightness, light</i>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b>of garments, <i>washed clean</i>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><a href='S:metaphorically'>metaph.</a> <i>bright, joyous</i>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>conspicuous</i>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>3. </b><a href='S:Adverb'>adv.</a> <el>-νῶς</el> <i>perspicuously;</i> <a href='S:Superlative'>Sup.</a> <el>φανότατα</el>, <b><a href='S:Lucian'>Luc.</a></b><p/></div> <hr/> <el><b>φανός2</b></el> <el>(φᾱνός, οῦ, ὁ,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:φάω'><el>φάω</el></a>\n<p/><i>a torch</i> of vine-twigs, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b>; <a href='S:confer, compare'>cf.</a> <el>πᾱνός.</el>,<p/>"}]}